measurements.description:
Eight flowers on one 76-cm inflorescence; 
  sepals and petals pale yellow, blushed brick distally, dark burgundy spots and markings;
   lip pale yellow, picotee, heavily overlaid uneven dark burgundy-red blotches;
   column pale yellow, blushed and overlaid dark burgundy, dark burgundy spots, anther cap pale yellow, small burgundy markings;
   substance very hard;
 texture matte.
